                                        "ma_el_slider_delay": "5000"
                                    },
                                    "elements": [
                                        {
                                            "id": "61084344",
                                            "settings": {
                                                "title": "What is included?",
                                                "header_size": "h4",
                                                "_animation": "fadeInUp"
                                            },
                                            "widgetType": "heading",
                                            "elType": "widget"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "id": "31ce3b05",
                                            "settings": {
                                                "editor": "<p>Whether you have a dripping faucet, a broken pipe, or a major water leak, we have the skills and expertise to fix the problem promptly. We use high-quality parts and materials to ensure that our repairs are long-lasting and effective.</p>\n<ul role=\"list\">\n<li><strong>Experienced plumbers:</strong> Our team of experienced and certified plumbers has the expertise to diagnose and repair any type of faucet or leak issue.</li>\n<li><strong>State-of-the-art equipment</strong>: We use the latest equipment and techniques to ensure that our repairs are efficient and effective.</li>\n<li><strong>Prompt service:</strong> We understand that faucet and leak issues can cause stress and inconvenience. That's why we offer prompt and reliable services to minimize disruption to your daily routine.</li>\n</ul>\n<div>\u00a0</div>\n<p>Don't let a faucet or leak issue ruin your day. Contact Plumby for professional faucet and leak repair services that you can count on. Call us today to schedule an appointment or request emergency plumbing services.</p>",
                                                "paragraph_spacing": {
                                                    "unit": "px",
                                                    "size": 35,
                                                    "sizes": []
                                                },
                                                "_animation": "fadeInUp"
                                            },
                                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                                            "elType": "widget"
                                        }
